import React from 'react';
import { Navbar, Nav, Container, Badge } from 'react-bootstrap';
import { LinkContainer } from 'react-router-bootstrap';
import { FaRobot, FaChartLine, FaExclamationTriangle, FaSearch, FaInfo, FaServer } from 'react-icons/fa';

const Navigation = ({ isConnected = false }) => {
  return (
    <Navbar bg="dark" variant="dark" expand="lg" sticky="top">
      <Container>
        <LinkContainer to="/">
          <Navbar.Brand>
            <FaRobot className="me-2" />
            LogBERT Hadoop RCA
            <Badge 
              bg={isConnected ? "success" : "danger"} 
              className="ms-2"
            >
              {isConnected ? "Online" : "Offline"}
            </Badge>
          </Navbar.Brand>
        </LinkContainer>
        
        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
        <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
          <Nav className="ms-auto">
            <LinkContainer to="/">
              <Nav.Link>
                <FaChartLine className="me-1" />
                Dashboard
              </Nav.Link>
            </LinkContainer>
            
            <LinkContainer to="/analysis">
              <Nav.Link>
                <FaSearch className="me-1" />
                Log Analysis
              </Nav.Link>
            </LinkContainer>
            
            <LinkContainer to="/anomaly-detection">
              <Nav.Link>
                <FaExclamationTriangle className="me-1" />
                Anomaly Detection
              </Nav.Link>
            </LinkContainer>
            
            <LinkContainer to="/root-cause-analysis">
              <Nav.Link>
                <FaRobot className="me-1" />
                Root Cause Analysis
              </Nav.Link>
            </LinkContainer>
            
            <LinkContainer to="/model-info">
              <Nav.Link>
                <FaInfo className="me-1" />
                Model Info
              </Nav.Link>
            </LinkContainer>
            
            <LinkContainer to="/api-status">
              <Nav.Link>
                <FaServer className="me-1" />
                API Status
              </Nav.Link>
            </LinkContainer>
          </Nav>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Container>
    </Navbar>
  );
};

export default Navigation;
